       A2  = (1S,2R,4aR)-1,2,4a,5-tetramethyl-1,2,3,4,4a,7,8,8a- octahydronaphthalen-1-yl or (1S,2R,4aR)-1,2,4a,5,5- pentamethyldecahydronaphthalen-1-yl; and
       R7  = H, -OH, 1-6C alkyl or -O-1-6C alkyl. 
